## GLOBAL SETTINGS ##

## Red Hat Zimbra ##
IMAPAccount redhat
Host mail.corp.redhat.com
User xiaofwan@redhat.com
AuthMechs GSSAPI
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/pki/ca-trust/source/anchors/Red_Hat_IT_Root_CA.crt

IMAPStore redhat-remote
Account redhat

MailDirStore redhat-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/redhat/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/redhat/Inbox
Flatten .

